#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.77"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.2"
msgid "8. Khajjanīyavagga"
msgstr "8. Itchy"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Dutiyaarahantasutta"
msgstr "77. The Perfected Ones (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.77:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;"
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self."

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.5"
msgid ""
"yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti … pe … evametaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And what’s not-self should be truly seen with proper understanding like this:"
" ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi "
"… saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, "
"feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn22.77:2.2"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn22.77:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’"

msgctxt "sn22.77:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yāvatā, bhikkhave, sattāvāsā, yāvatā bhavaggaṃ, ete aggā, ete seṭṭhā "
"lokasmiṃ yadidaṃ arahanto”ti."
msgstr ""
"As far as there are abodes of sentient beings, even up until the pinnacle of "
"existence, the perfected ones are the foremost and the best.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
